Prize winners

The following three studies by Fritz, Bondarenko and Kusnetsov, and Dolgov were awarded the first three prizes in the Szachy 1973 award. The study by Fritz was cooked and eliminated and the other two were therefore awarded prizes 1 and 2.

Here are three corrections. I consider the last onea version since only the beginning of the study is identical to the one by Dolgov.
